Body: MOMS AVENUE PRE-ICO STARTS ON DECEMBER 11TH 2017  Moms Avenue mission is to accelerate women entrepreneurship through a blockchain powered platform! Author: DroidR17A
Title: [ANN]MomsAvenue - Blockchain Platform For Women Entrepreneurship-New DAO and R&R
Body: I'm quite enthusiastic about the potential for this project and ICO, but I don't understand the token distribution model. Looking at the whitepaper and the pre and ICO token sales distribution, I'd like to better understand what happens with the remaining tokens.  If the total amount is 2,200,000,000  Pre-ico is 17,200,000  ICO is 862,800,000  And bounty allocation is 10,000,000  =890,000,000  That leaves 1,310,000,000 tokens.  According to the whitepaper, 50% is supposed to go to the community. How will the balance be distributed to the Moms Avenue community, and over what time period (e.g. how many years)? The whitepaper states a 12 month lock, but does that mean they could all hit the market after one year, causing a huge deflation in value, and how is that 50%? The math doesn't add up.  Please elaborate.

Author: Avenue
Title: [ANN]MomsAvenue - Blockchain Platform For Women Entrepreneurship-New DAO and R&R
Body: Regarding 50%. We are looking for a long-term deal with Community. Tokens in this list will not hit exchange or traded. These tokens could go to users via Rating and Reward system. Rewards will be managed by supply and demand principles to avoid impact on token price.  Our constrains Tokens will move from this pool via smart contacts only. Tokens from community development pool will be used for community development only. Tokens in community development pool will NOT be listed on Exchange. It will be a constraint not allowing to use more than 20% community development pool in 12 months period. Tokens usage will be balanced using supply and demand principles. Tokens will be accessible via Moms Avenue platform only.

Author: Avenue
Title: [ANN]MomsAvenue - Blockchain Platform For Women Entrepreneurship-New DAO and R&R
Body: We have begun a Smart Contract Code Audit campaign with a huge reward of 6,000,000 M.O.M. tokens. Use your experiences to audit, fix bugs, and find any other possible technical issues with Moms Avenue smart contracts. Discover them and get rewarded!  We have three reward types: • Critical bugs, which provide an ability to steal ether or tokens, will be rewarded with a 1,000,000 M.O.M. tokens! • Medium-severity bugs or improvements, which do not change balances, will be rewarded with 50,000 M.O.M. tokens. • Low severity bugs (improvements and optimisations) will get a reward of 10,000 M.O.M. tokens.  Every contribution must be constructive and valuable. Every accepted functionality improvement/bug/fix will get M.O.M Tokens as a reward.  Moms Avenue Smart Contracts: https://github.com/Moms-Avenue/smart-contracts Submit BUG here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/uiM3p5W0YE0y5zcl2  You will get information about rewards via email. Tokens will be sent to your ETH Wallet after the end of the Pre-ICO. Estimated time of delivery — 4 weeks.  If you have any further questions, feel free to contact in Telegram group — https://t.me/momsavenue and hi@momsavenue.com
